# The apparatus is tracked (docs/ARM-ALTRA.md §Repository layout, tasks/109); its
# build and measurement outputs are not.
target/

# Stage evidence is written here on the box. Raw per-sample volume too large for
# git is content-addressed with a checked-in manifest, summary and reproduction
# command (§Evidence integrity) — so the manifests land, the raw sample dumps do
# not.
results/**/raw/

# AA-1(c) bulk runs carry ~250k records each (~100 MB). The raw per-sample dump is
# too large for git; it stays on the box, content-addressed by the manifest's
# `records_sha256`, graded there, and its floor-check verdict is what lands. The
# run-set.json manifest (small) beside it is still tracked (§Evidence integrity).
results/aa-1c/*-bulk/records.jsonl
